Changelog for the 'x509' cookbook, and the 'chef-ssl-client' gem.

Version 1.2.0
 
 * Add support for the revoke and gencrl commands. (Michael Hart)

Version 1.1.0

 * Switch to secure rubygems source to avoid deprecation warning from
   Bundler (Doug Barth)

 * Optionally add the CA certificate into the deployed certificate
   file. (Arnold Krille)

 * Add not_before and not_after dates into the certificate databag
   (Arnold Krille)

 * Avoid crashing on bad node data (Michael Hart)

 * Work around lack of Base64.urlsafe_encode64 on Ruby 1.8
   (Holger Just)

